{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was like-- so no more apples.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, we-- we took tremendous chances, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you start realizing what-- what I did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember one time, I picked up 10 boxes of strawberries to bring into the commandant.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the-- Theresienstadt was very unique.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle, that's where the commandant was because that's where their barrack was and that's where their clubs were.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the middle of the camp was never bombed, all right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's where they had their-- they had all the records there, they had-- the kasernes had name after countries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in the Hamburger Kaserne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was Hanover and the-- and the-- What's a kaserne?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A kaserne is a barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a permanent barrack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought-- those were known as kasernes, you know, permanent barracks, huge buildings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so where was I?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was in different-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- and the Germans had the Sudeten barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where they kept all the records from all over Europe was kept there, you know, where-- how many people and things like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also where the commandant was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So now I'm bringing in those 10 cases of strawberries and I look.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no amount written on the slip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a guy with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, two cases.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Take off the minute we get inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we went inside the camp and then into the-- there was another gate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took off the two cases, two boxes, you know they're typical boxes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't realize what kind of a score that was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people were crawling to me, give me a strawberry, give me a this and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how I got a wristwatch.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
